				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/Bi%E1%BB%87t-%C4%91i%E1%BB%87u-kh%C3%BAc-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-zNcPtbAhidloxKfdAOQCeA">Biệt điệu khúc kỳ 2 - 别調曲其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%E1%BA%A1-Tr%C4%83n/author-1SPKfkHlUAnw6r-glqobvQ">Tạ Trăn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/B%E1%BB%99c-b%E1%BB%91/poem-eKE3xqXFYgjByUHRCL9W8w">Bộc bố - 瀑布</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Jingak-Hyesim/author-RGxtMe1sV6AuAbjteu9Sdg">Jingak Hyesim</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-B%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4/D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-li%E1%BB%85u-chi-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-04/poem-enns_JNsQf_NFaE_NKnjBw">Dương liễu chi từ kỳ 04 - 楊柳枝詞其四</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-B%C3%ADch-Ng%C3%B4/author-fQmiCgisar9fVuxwxCv_kQ">Lê Bích Ngô</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-hao-h%C3%A0nh/poem-2zNLpREgSBc0Oe7oXzK5MQ">Đại tường thượng hao hành - 大牆上蒿行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Phi/author-_plJ3nwj8cVN02KPZ4P_8g">Tào Phi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/%C4%90%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng-c%E1%BB%91-ki%E1%BB%83m-hi%E1%BB%87u-c%C3%B4ng-b%E1%BB%99-vi%C3%AAn-ngo%E1%BA%A1i-lang-%C4%90%E1%BB%97-qu%C3%A2n-m%E1%BB%99-h%E1%BB%87-minh/poem-A6qN_vao7Go6vLRVhh8KVA">Đường cố kiểm hiệu công bộ viên ngoại lang Đỗ quân mộ hệ minh - 唐故檢校工部員外郎杜君墓系銘</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%C3%AAn-Ch%E1%BA%A9n/author-bMSP5YOXWyK1jTzTI9MKNQ">Nguyên Chẩn</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/Nh%C3%A0n-t%C3%ACnh-ph%C3%BA/poem-SfJjdY1BShl5c2Q2RpHH7g">Nhàn tình phú - 閑情賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%C3%A0o-Ti%E1%BB%81m/author-y4iJ6v3mYp-Z_KEorcHd_g">Đào Tiềm</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-M%E1%BB%A5c/Th%E1%BA%ADp-c%E1%BB%